{"tid":1222863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[Respect]克警有善對待記者，直得支持","createTime":"2019-06-14T14:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T14:29:08.000Z","uid":4903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"49add430f3e1e052831fa7af85f11b057ce5e001","tid":1222863,"uid":4903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T14:29:08.000Z","msg":"警務處處長盧偉聰召開記者會表示，警方喺金鐘一帶驅趕示威者中，佢保證警方一定克制，下文以「<span style=\"color: red;\">克警</span>」(克制的警察)簡稱。由於克警對暴徒使用「低殺傷力武器」係絕對正確，無可置疑會對示威者造成傷害，而記者身份係中立，咁我哋可以睇下佢哋點樣有善對待記者朋友，以支持及客觀觀察克警今次行動如何揚威國際。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 記你老母</span></strong><br />\n記掛住人哋個老母，連我都冇咁大愛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />商台記者喺採訪時多次表明記者身份，仍遭警員揮棍多次推撞，商台記者已清楚講明自己係記者，但其中一個克警回應﹕「記你老母！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uB35ULrr1PE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuB35ULrr1PE&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=512896ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uB35ULrr1PE</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.dcard.tw/oUXKPDq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.dcard.tw%2FoUXKPDq.jpg&h=e3bcc8f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">2. 請記者朋友食好西</span></strong><br />\n記者朋友，平時出街食飯食得多都厭啦，胡椒噴霧同催淚彈試過未吖?不如試下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YczQNCb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYczQNCb.gif&h=84e773bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190614/large/a0401b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190614%2Flarge%2Fa0401b.gif&h=7da8e73a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n法國記者朋友向克警講「You shoot the journalist motherfucker!」「This is still Hong Kong, not China, not yet」「You don&rsquo;t play the rule, you should be arrested」「Xi Jingping will love you」，克警對你哋咁有善，又請催淚彈放題，係咪應該用返中文同克警溝通，等佢哋明白你講咩嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190613/large/1560363690_f43f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190613%2Flarge%2F1560363690_f43f.jpg&h=1c685703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iTIqDFPjypU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiTIqDFPjypU&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=e68198b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iTIqDFPjypU</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">3. 放過懷疑藏有攻擊性武器的記者</span></strong><br />\n立場新聞記者林彥邦拍攝克警清場時，被克警多次用盾牌推撞背部，當佢拿出採訪證並向警方展示，「我持有政府認可傳媒機構採訪證，我完全無意阻礙警方行動，但我想問，到底你哋條防線去到邊？你話我知我就會退去防線後面」，一名克警只一直重覆「我睇唔清楚」，大佬啊夜媽媽睇唔清好正常啫，咁黑嘅環境冇變成黑暗中的警察已經好好，至於懷疑林藏有攻擊性武器(5支1.5公升水)，好彩，克警喺懷疑底下都選揮放行佢，冇帶返警署調查，哇五支水咁危險都唔的你返差館，仲唔多謝克警?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%87%B7%E7%96%91%E6%88%91%E8%97%8F%E6%9C%89%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A%E6%80%A7%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8-%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E6%9C%89%E5%92%81%E5%A4%9A%E6%B0%B4-%E4%BF%82%E5%92%AA%E8%A6%81%E9%BB%8E%E6%8E%9F%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2587%25B7%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2588%2591%25E8%2597%258F%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2594%25BB%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%2599%25A8-%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2592%2581%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%25B0%25B4-%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%2592%25AA%25E8%25A6%2581%25E9%25BB%258E%25E6%258E%259F%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2593%258B%2F&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=2ff90c29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%2587%25B7%25E7%2596%2591%25E6%2588%2591%25E8%2597%258F%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2594%25BB%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%2599%25A8-%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%2592%2581%25E5%25A4%259A%25E6%25B0%25B4-%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%2592%25AA%25E8%25A6%2581%25E9%25BB%258E%25E6%258E%259F%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2593%258B%2F&h=56fb4c49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E6%87%B7%E7%96%91%E6%88%91%E8%97%8F%E6%9C%89%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A%E6%80%A7%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8-%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E6%9C%89%E5%92%81%E5%A4%9A%E6%B0%B4-%E4%BF%82%E5%92%AA%E8%A6%81%E9%BB%8E%E6%8E%9F%E6%88%91%E5%93%8B/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">4. 畀記者朋友休息一下</span></strong><br />\n「大批防暴警員持盾牌由立法會前進添馬公園，數百警員前往龍和道驅趕示威者，並利用閃燈照向記者的眼部及攝影鏡頭，企圖阻止採訪，並將記者趕向添華道，同時將趕向示威添馬公園摩天輪方向，示威者趕向搬動鐵馬頑抗」<br />\n盧sir話克警真係有個heart、有心去做好同傳媒嘅關係，講得一啲都冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有部分克警工作超過30小時，身心疲倦，所以佢哋好明白記者工作都好辛苦，咪用一啲閃燈射記者朋友囉，阿媽都有教啦，夜晚唔開燈睇嘢好傷眼呀。同埋克警用心良苦，想記者朋友唔好成日掛住拍攝而唔休息。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2893938/org/109cfc748b91c389e7ea23a06c56fec0.jpg/8MkHiW0XzohUQIEiofvQrD7JhnCB5Iv8HrLJOzSyyTs?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2893938%2Forg%2F109cfc748b91c389e7ea23a06c56fec0.jpg%2F8MkHiW0XzohUQIEiofvQrD7JhnCB5Iv8HrLJOzSyyTs%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=1ae47538&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/338646/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E9%A9%85%E6%95%A3%E9%BE%8D%E5%92%8C%E9%81%93%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E9%96%83%E7%87%88%E5%B0%84%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E9%8F%A1%E9%A0%AD%E9%98%BB%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F338646%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E9%25A9%2585%25E6%2595%25A3%25E9%25BE%258D%25E5%2592%258C%25E9%2581%2593%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585-%25E9%2596%2583%25E7%2587%2588%25E5%25B0%2584%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%258F%25A1%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E9%2598%25BB%25E6%258E%25A1%25E8%25A8%25AA&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3PjZriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=ae5ab1ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/338646/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E9%A9%85%E6%95%A3%E9%BE%8D%E5%92%8C%E9%81%93%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85-%E9%96%83%E7%87%88%E5%B0%84%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E9%8F%A1%E9%A0%AD%E9%98%BB%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有太多太多不能盡錄，歡迎大家補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我知今次事件有記者朋友話克警唔啱，但希望睇完呢個po後可以放低成見，用你哋最犀利嘅武器(文字)去繼續宣揚克警嘅有善啦。而且盧sir話會加強訓練，冀警員更理解記者工作困難，所以大家相信克警啦。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">支持支持! Respect respect!</span></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/74206.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F74206.png&h=fbc6409e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}